high_descs: Go to the kitchen area to your left, stopping at the counters to the left of the sink ahead.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Look down at the potato on the same counter.
Slice the potato with the knife.
Go to the sink to the right.
Place the knife into the sink.
Return to the sliced potato.
Pick up one potato slice from the counter.
Go back to the sink again.
Rinse the potato slice off with water and pick it back up.
Turn around and approach the microwave opposite the sink.
Put the potato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, wash one slice with water and place that slice in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter top beside the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter top.
Turn to the potato on the  counter top to the left.
Slice the potato on the counter top.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn left and go to the potato on the counter top beside the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from the middle.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Place the potato in the sink, wash the potato, and pick it back up.
Turn around to the red microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean slice of potato in the microwave.
